    {"id":"K010","project_id":"baum_mobile","furniture_id":"baum-yatai","scope":"production","type":"howto","title":"ポンジ生地のシワ・たるみ対策","content":"ポンジ生地はシワが入るのでお手入れ大変。袋縫製の方はピンと貼ってるけど裏側は弛んでしまう。\nパネル（ステンレンボードorアルポリ複合版）の方がブランドイメージ的にもおすすめ。マジックテープで取り付け、取り回しも楽。","posted_by":"黒部駿人","channel":"#3040_baum","date":"2026-03-27","slack_url":"https://vuild.slack.com/archives/C09V70VFF96/p1774593045137429","images":["photos/knowledge/baum/IMG_7262.jpg","photos/knowledge/baum/IMG_7263.jpg","photos/knowledge/baum/IMG_7264.jpg","photos/knowledge/baum/IMG_7265.jpg","photos/knowledge/baum/IMG_7266.jpg","photos/knowledge/baum/IMG_7267.jpg"],"edited":false},
    {"id":"K011","project_id":null,"furniture_id":"town-unit-sq900","scope":"production","type":"trouble","title":"MDF加工時のシートコーティング剥離","content":"MDFにはシートコーティングがあり、ShopBotでポケット加工するとコーティングが剥がれてしまう。レール部分の加工方法を検討する必要あり。金子が塗装後に水に浸けて耐水性テストを実施。","posted_by":"黒部駿人","channel":"#3039_yokohamanarureweek2025","date":"2025-01-29","slack_url":"https://vuild.slack.com/archives/C086FBQ1EN4/p1738125948231859","images":[],"edited":false},
